// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-3139 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: 8e503830-7553-5a1e-b256-1cf7e16cec61

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:12.04*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:14.04*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:15.04*")
